OL,5,EWHAT I REALLY, REALLY WANTGby Faith,   
OL,6,G13, Hawick HIgh School                 
OL,7,BEvery break and lunchtime I see them. I
OL,8,Bsee them laughing with each other and  
OL,9,Bhaving a good time. Then there is me. I
OL,10,Bstand in the corner just watching them,
OL,11,Blonging to be part of them.            
OL,13,BSometimes my eyes fill with tears, so I
OL,14,Bturn to the wall, so that no one will  
OL,15,Bsee. I don't know why I do it, nobody  
OL,16,Bever does, because nobody cares.       
OL,18,BSo can you tell what I really, really  
OL,19,Bwant?                                  
