OL,5,EWHAT I REALLY, REALLY WANTGby K Harris,
OL,6, 16, Pontarddulais School, South Wales  
OL,7,BWhat I really really want is to grow up
OL,8,Bmaybe get married, have one or two     
OL,9,Bchildren, to have a job writing books, 
OL,10,Bpoetry and maybe the odd song. It's a  
OL,11,Bfuture I will always long for.         
OL,12,B                                       
OL,13,BA stable home, by the sea, watching the
OL,14,Bwaves hitting the bank, in sunny       
OL,15,BCalifornia. I'd really like to help    
OL,16,Bpeople, so I'd open a homeless centre, 
OL,17,Band help poor homeless animals. I want 
OL,18,Bto give people my care and have a happy
OL,19,Bfuture, that's fair.                   
