OL,4,G````````````BSECONDARYG``````Su;/!G    
OL,5,EWHAT I REALLY, REALLY WANTGby Sita, 13,
OL,6,GThe Broadway, Perry Barr, Birmingham   
OL,7,BIf you asked a poor kid, "What would   
OL,8,Byou like?" he would probably reply     
OL,9,B"mountain bike." If you asked a        
OL,10,Bstarving kid "What do you need?" she   
OL,11,Bwould probably say "filling feed."     
OL,12,B                                       
OL,13,BIf you ask a crying kid "Do you want a 
OL,14,Btoy?" after saying yes, he'd be a      
OL,15,Blaughing boy.                          
OL,17,BIf you happened to meet and did you ask
OL,18,Bme: "What do you really, really want?" 
OL,19,BI'd say "to be HAPPY."                 
