OL,5,EWHAT I REALLY, REALLY WANTGby Katy, 14,
OL,6,GChase Terrace High School, Staffs.     
OL,7,BA dragon raises its magnificent head.  
OL,8,BEyes, cold glittering shards of        
OL,9,Bintelligence. A hero, tall and proud,  
OL,10,Bface impassive. The battle begins, a   
OL,11,Bslow dance of death, a dance performed 
OL,12,Bdown the ages. Good and evil.          
OL,14,BThe icy cold waters of reality close in
OL,15,Bon me because of a demanding knocking. 
OL,16,BStretching, I ease my cramped muscles, 
OL,17,Bgrimacing. I can't complain. I picked  
OL,18,Bthis life as a writer ` something I've 
OL,19,Balways really, really wanted.          
